<div class="p-5 text-center">
  <h1 class="text-info">Bootstrap Examples</h1>
  <p class="text-primary">Bootstrap is the css framework that's being used to style and layout most of this website. Below are some examples of bootstrap components that can be used when developing a website.</p>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid p-5 bg-body-inverse-tertiary text-secondary">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 m-0 my-auto">
            <div id="AutoPlayingCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner rounded">
                  <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/img/Puffin-In-Flight.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Puffin in flight">
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/Hedgehog.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Hedgehog under bushes">
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/Eider-Duck.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Eider duck flapping wings on the sea">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#AutoPlayingCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                  <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#AutoPlayingCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                  <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
              </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 m-0 px-5 py-3 py-lg-0 text-center">
            <h2>Carousels</h2>
            <p class="pt-4">These are two examples of bootstrap carousels.</p>
            <p class="pt-2">The carousel on the left is autoplaying so it goes through each slide automatically. It's also possible to go through the images with the arrow buttons, although they can be removed.</p>
            <p class="pt-2">The carousel on the right has extra indicators which show position and are interactive. Text can also be overlayed on top of the images.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 m-0 my-auto">
            <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide">
                <div class="carousel-indicators">
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-inner rounded">
                  <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/img/Hut.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Stone hut in the Yorkshire Dales, near Kettlewell">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Yorkshire Dales</h5>
                        <p>Stone hut near Kettlewell</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/Lamb.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Lamb on limbstone pavement, Yorkshire Dales">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Yorkshire Dales</h5>
                        <p>Lambs above Gordale Scar</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/Malham-Sunset.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Sunset at the top of Malham Cove">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Yorkshire Dales</h5>
                        <p>Sunset on top of Malham Cove</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
                  <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
                  <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
              </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

